{"id": 1831, "genre": 1001, "title": "这些年你都心甘情愿交过哪些懒人税？", "description": "懒人税，即，因为懒而多花的钱，可能是懒得做消费功课，也可能是抱着省时省力的心愿买了一堆鸡肋。", "record_count": 3480, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170803154520TOFy56JrkNlU1DHM.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-08-07T03:00:23Z", "options": [{"id": 228096, "content": "肥胖。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1091493}, {"id": 228097, "content": "外卖", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 401463}, {"id": 229123, "content": "坐出租车上班", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1103528}, {"id": 232452, "content": "外送费吧……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 746748}, {"id": 228104, "content": "滴滴", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1061542}, {"id": 228108, "content": "因为懒，纱窗坏了不修空调没氟不修洗衣机入水口水管断了不修，导致大夏天屋里进蚊虫，室内持续高温，洗衣服手动接水来回倒。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1099810}, {"id": 228112, "content": "氪金", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1022401}, {"id": 231697, "content": "小费", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1114972}, {"id": 228114, "content": "健身卡，外卖", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1099840}, {"id": 228371, "content": "主修课不想上，找人去，一次20", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1101225}, {"id": 228116, "content": "不上班", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1010440}, {"id": 228117, "content": "懒得自己锻炼，报了健身房...结果还懒得去", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1099879}, {"id": 228122, "content": "花3块钱买了无广告的好奇心日报。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1099950}, {"id": 230938, "content": "外卖，购物。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1111223}, {"id": 230428, "content": "有一次一个人乘火车回家，带了个大行李箱挺重，但不是完全提不动；结果到了检票口经不住诱惑话二十块请了个小红帽，最后发现下了扶梯其实也就一小段路╮( •́ω•̀ )╭", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1108885}, {"id": 228127, "content": "就是不想动", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1099991}, {"id": 228639, "content": "充手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1095541}, {"id": 228128, "content": "懒得找百度云资源宁可不看?", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1100009}, {"id": 228133, "content": "外卖", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1089530}, {"id": 228390, "content": "在马云爸爸那里买的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1101268}, {"id": 228136, "content": "外卖，网购超重费", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1043839}, {"id": 230952, "content": "家政服务", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 941792}, {"id": 228137, "content": "见过师兄买过一大把一次性筷子…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1094841}, {"id": 228138, "content": "在方便面袋子里倒开水吃泡面。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1094841}, {"id": 227884, "content": "外卖", "image": null, "praise_count": 1023, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1098895}, {"id": 227885, "content": "健身没动力时报的私教课", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 726311}, {"id": 227886, "content": "懒得在网上找盗版游戏资源、打补丁杀病毒，入坑steam。", "image": null, "praise_count": 71, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1004548}, {"id": 227887, "content": "懒得在网上找盗版游戏资源，直接在steam上买", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1004548}, {"id": 227888, "content": "电脑整机一大坑，因为不想自己组装，为此多所付出至少30%的钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1095941}, {"id": 227889, "conte